SEARS, ROEBUCK AND COMPANY, petitioner,
v.
Larry BUTLER, et al., Individually and on Behalf of All Others Similarly Situated. No. 13-430. Supreme Court of the United States Feb. 24, 2014. Case below, 727 F.3d 796 .
